{
  "texts": [
    "The follow-ing is a summary of the challenging issues that need to be investigated:1) IAD dataset should be gathered from actual manufacturing lines, not labs.",
    "The public cannot access the real-world anomalous dataset due to privacy concerns.The majority of open-source IAD datasets generate anomalies from anomaly-free products.",
    "In other words, the abnormalities from open-source IAD datasets may not occur in actual production lines, which makes deploying IADs in industrial manufacturing very challenging.2) It is challenging to enable the creation of a unified IAD model in the absence of multiple domain IAD datasets.",
    "Recently, You et al. [4] propose a unified IAD model for multiple class objects.",
    "However, they disregard the notion that commodities produced in the same plant should be of the same sort."
  ]
}